          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Produce All Relevant Information to Safeguard Climate Act or the PARIS Climate Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of State to report quarterly to Congress on whether any parties to the Paris Agreement to limit greenhouse gas emissions have&nbsp;indicated intention to withdraw from the agreement, and whether the United States has established specific terms for reengagement with the agreement. The report shall be publicly available on the State Department's website. <br /></p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-12-06T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
